name: Mike Huckabee
bio: Host of "Huckabee" on TBN,Fox News contributor, Author, Podcaster, Fmr AR Gov, Bass Guitarist, grandfather to 6 cutest kids in world!

social_posts.post_text:
We’re coming up on three years since the COVID-19 pandemic began. Scientists quickly developed reliable COVID tests that are now cheap, plentiful and available at any drug store. So how come Medicare spent $1.5 billion on COVID tests in 2020 during the full crush of the pandemic, $2 billion on tests in all of 2021, and another $2 billion just through October of 2022? Why are we spending more and more money on tests that are cheaper and less needed?

If you suspect that it might have something to do with fraud, political connections and the government throwing around big piles of money without proper oversight, then you pass the IQ test.
Sunrise on the Sea of Galilee yesterday. Never grows old.
Join me for the trip of a lifetime.
In Ft Worth to see the incomparable @Skynyrd band w/ ZZ Top & Uncle Kracker.  Best rock album?  God & Guns by Lynyrd Skynyrd.  Rock on!
When visiting Ft Worth don’t miss the John Wayne Museum in the Stockyards.  The Duke was an American original!
In Hope, Arkansas with Janet to celebrate our 50th Hope High School Class Reunion.  Who are all these old people showing up for this?
Glad the GOP House finally got down to business & they made an excellent choice in Rep. Mike Johnson for Speaker.  Now, go do the Lord's work in the Devil's town!

I’m just returning home from a very intense trip to Israel where I joined some other evangelical leaders in 3 days of meetings with Israeli officials, families of those who were kidnapped and taken hostage by Hamas terrorists, and survivors of the savage and barbaric attacks on innocent civilians, including babies, young mothers, elderly people, and teenagers.
Duck season resumed in Arkansas today & was a great day hunting at 5 Oaks Lodge-got limits of Mallards in just under an hour. Arkansas is duck hunting capital of the world!
I hope to see you there!
